# Icon Component Rule

The [Icon.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Icon.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- Single File Component (SFC) in `src/components/ui`.
- Used for rendering SVG icons from the `lucide-vue-next` icon set.
- Accepts `name` (icon name), `className` (for custom classes), and `strokeWidth` props.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for sizing and utility classes.
- Dynamically renders the icon component based on the `name` prop.

For icon best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Icon documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/icon) as a reference.


